text: Cynthia McKinney (born March 17, 1955) is an American politician. She was born in Atlanta, Georgia. She was the 2008 presidential candidate for the Green Party. She was a member of the U.S. House of Representatives from Georgia from 1993 until 2003 and again from 2005 until 2007. ==References== Category:1955 births Category:Living people Category:African-American politicians Category:Democratic Party (United States) politicians Category:Politicians from Atlanta Category:United States representatives from Georgia Category:Green Party of the United States politicians
